{"segment_id": "shangshu-012-shang-shu-speech-of-tang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-012-shang-shu-speech-of-tang", "source_id": "shangshu-012-shang-shu-speech-of-tang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·商書 湯誓 [5]", "text_original": "夏師敗績，湯遂從之，遂伐三朡，俘厥寶玉。誼伯、仲伯作《典寶》。", "text_normalized": "夏師敗績，湯遂從之，遂伐三朡，俘厥寶玉。誼伯、仲伯作《典寶》。", "notes": ""}
